        <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch74s08.html#MonstersVermin21">Monstrous centipedes</a> have a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a> checks, and a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills179">Hide</a> checks. They can use either their Strength or Dexterity modifier for <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks, whichever is higher. <a href="ch74s09.html#MonstersVermin24">Monstrous scorpions</a> can take 10 on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks, even if threatened or distracted.</p>
